 (symmetric objects), and synthetic texture-free CAD renders, measuring not only keypoint reprojection error but also calibration of uncertainty estimates (via proper scoring rules) and generalization to unseen poses. The framework has broad implications for robotics, where reliable uncertainty quantification improves decision-making in grasping and pose estimation.",
